text: Osinovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Klyapovskoye Rural Settlement, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 20 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located on the Taz River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
title: Osinovo, Perm Krai
